Final Project

Downloading through terminal

Step 0: Note the following Kilter Board App account information: (Will be necessary moving forward)
    username: kiltergpt4900
    password: COMP4900!

Step 1: Clone the BoardLib github repo by running the following line in the terminal:
git clone https://github.com/lemeryfertitta/BoardLib.git

Step 2: Download the database using the following line
python -m boardlib database kilter kilter_board.db --username <input_kilterboard_username>

    ie. python -m boardlib database kilter kilter_board.db --username kiltergpt4900

Step 3: User will be prompted to enter a password to sync the database, enter your password for the kilter board account above. (COMP4900!)

Step 4 (Optional): Once downloaded, the user may run extract_routes.py to extract the database into a .csv file. (Used for training)

Step 4.1 (Optional): Run gpt.py to train the model.

Step 5: Run create_route.py to create a route, displaying it on a web browser.